ound the conceptions about gender in the community of OpenStreetMap, we\'re launching this survey in order to make an analysis on the role, representation and participation of women in OSM, and in this way to find a way to close the gender gap within the community.\n\nWe invite all OSM contributors to fill out this survey and help us to gather information in the most complete and diverse way possible. We also look forward to your comments through the HT <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/geochicas\"><strong>#Geochicas</strong></a><strong> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/osmintegra\">#OSMintegra</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/OSMintegrates?src=hash\">#OSMintegrates</a></strong> on your different social networks and in that way enable discussions around this activity.\n<blockquote>We want to thank all the people who helped translate this survey, this will help us reach out to more communities and gather more information.</blockquote>\nFormulario  de encuesta / Survey form\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScoTUj4HP2-KOH58pku7zkRmK843uXWhN7o_UazepfH2DbzKA/viewform\">Español</a></strong></li>\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf2-MoTnCgqc3Jnu1zValuh6enKzR_049k1aAQtR2sl9qEJsw/viewform?usp=sf_link\">English</a></strong></li>\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdHDUr4Gstrs8BqKEdbYs8gZznXR2_0leZMsSAwuo5Jo0LFaw/viewform?usp=sf_link\">Française</a></strong></li>\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScCNcfihYSwHYIyZoP9Lc4ihBsVUd2b-i99ktSuAauZeoKfJA/viewform?usp=sf_link\">Deutsche</a></strong></li>\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdWUdp_GmCqmjRu8p0ufX6z5zfP4fgDBSDDTlJhVzZTm1i9yg/viewform\">ελληνικά</a></strong></li>\n 	<li><strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeJMYwvH3isV6hRE39RWsAjGaLfjRKvm26bveYeqXTSQFvXHg/viewform?usp=sf_link\">Português</a></strong></li>\n 	<li><strong><a